						               													<description>Zombie Mosh puts you in the role of a human survivor or the walking undead in a table top environment, using your scenery and miniatures. It takes place during modern times.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game-play consists of the sides (survivors and zombies) taking turns with move, shoot and melee phases. The game uses 6 sided dice for all outcomes. There are rules for over 30 different weapons to kill the zombies with and rules for vehicle movement and running down zombies with. There are also several scenarios to use which include maps and modifying suggestions to make each scenario more replayable. Each scenario has different goals and set ups. With these rules it would be easy to play out any scene from any of your favorite zombie movies. There are also all of the markers and templates needed to play included.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Everything is in full color. It is available in pdf format at this time and has 56 pages. Was originally written in 2007, 2.0 was released in 2008 and 2.5 was released in 2011. There is a rumor of a 3.0  release.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
